<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gab's Scrapbook</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&family=Homemade+Apple&family=Special+Elite&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #e6dfcf;
            --ink: #2b2621;
            --sage-tape: rgba(135, 169, 130, 0.4);
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/papyrus.png');
            color: var(--ink);
            font-family: 'Special Elite', serif;
            margin: 0; padding: 40px;
            display: flex; justify-content: center;
        }

        .scrapbook {
            display: grid;
            /* Column 1: About Me | Column 2: 100px GAP | Column 3: Songs */
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 100px 1.2fr;
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        header { grid-column: 1 / -1; text-align: center; padding-bottom: 40px; }
        header h1 { font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive; font-size: 5.5rem; margin: 0; }

        /* --- TOP ARTISTS (No changes to this section) --- */
        .artist-gallery {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .polaroid {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px 15px 35px 15px;
            box-shadow: 3px 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            width: 160px;
            position: relative;
            transition: 0.4s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .polaroid img { width: 100%; height: 160px; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
        .polaroid p { font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive; font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 10px 0 0 0; text-align: center; }

        .polaroid-info {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0; 
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            opacity: 0; transition: 0.3s; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.75rem;
            z-index: 5;
        }
        .polaroid:hover .polaroid-info { opacity: 1; }
        .polaroid:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }

        /* --- PAPER SCRAPS --- */
        .paper-scrap {
            background: #fdfaf0;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: relative;
        }
        .tape {
            position: absolute; width: 70px; height: 25px;
            background: var(--sage-tape);
            top: -12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-2deg);
        }

        /* About Me Section */
        .about-section { grid-column: 1; transform: rotate(-1deg); height: fit-content; }
        .about-section h3 { font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive; margin-top: 0; }

        /* Favorite Songs Section with Hover */
        .songs-section { grid-column: 3; transform: rotate(1deg); }
        .song-card {
            display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px dotted #ccc; padding-bottom: 15px;
            cursor: help;
        }
        .song-card img { width: 65px; height: 65px; border-radius: 4px; transition: 0.3s; }
        
        .song-desc { 
            font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.4;
            max-height: 0; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }
        .song-card:hover .song-desc { max-height: 100px; opacity: 1; margin-top: 5px; }
        .song-card:hover img { transform: scale(1.1); }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .scrapbook { display: block; }
            .paper-scrap { margin-bottom: 50px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="scrapbook">
    <header>
        <h1>Gabriel</h1>
        <p>— A soul full of stories and dreams —</p>
    </header>

    <div class="artist-gallery">
        <div class="polaroid" style="transform: rotate(-2deg);">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/Clairo.jpg" alt="Clairo">
            <p>Clairo</p>
            <div class="polaroid-info">Bedroom pop that feels like a warm hug.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid" style="transform: rotate(3deg);">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/CocteuTwins.jpg" alt="Cocteau Twins">
            <p>Cocteau Twins</p>
            <div class="polaroid-info">Architects of ethereal dream pop.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid" style="transform: rotate(-1deg);">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/FleetwoodMac.jpg" alt="Fleetwood Mac">
            <p>Fleetwood Mac</p>
            <div class="polaroid-info">Legendary rock with timeless harmonies.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid" style="transform: rotate(4deg);">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/WeyesBlood.jpg" alt="Weyes Blood">
            <p>Weyes Blood</p>
            <div class="polaroid-info">Cinematic, baroque pop with an old-soul feel.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid" style="transform: rotate(-3deg);">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/MattMaltese.jpg" alt="Matt Maltese">
            <p>Matt Maltese</p>
            <div class="polaroid-info">Dry wit and beautiful piano ballads.</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <article class="paper-scrap about-section">
        <div class="tape"></div>
        <h3>About Me</h3>
        <p>Hello! I'm <strong>Gabriel</strong>, A soul learning the art of healing, currently in her second year of nursing.</p>
        <p>I enjoy listening to music, binge-watching films, and sleeping.</p>
        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px dashed #ccc; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p style="font-style: italic; font-size: 0.85rem;">
            "Love isn't something that weak people do. Being a romantic takes a hell of a lot of hope."<br>
            <span style="font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive; display: block; margin-top: 5px;">— Fleabag</span>
        </p>
    </article>

    <div style="grid-column: 2;"></div>

    <article class="paper-scrap songs-section">
        <div class="tape"></div>
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive;">Favorite Songs</h3>
        
        <div class="song-card">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/harbor.jpg" alt="Harbor">
            <div>
                <strong>Harbor — Clairo</strong>
                <div class="song-desc">Realizing a relationship’s end while still being an emotional anchor.</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="song-card">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/rilkeanheart.jpg" alt="Rilkean Heart">
            <div>
                <strong>Rilkean Heart — Cocteau Twins</strong>
                <div class="song-desc">A shimmering, poetic dream about intense connection.</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="song-card">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/f8c01717babdbb0a51867d5b9086e5143328f682/images/Andromeda.jpg" alt="Andromeda">
            <div>
                <strong>Andromeda — Weyes Blood</strong>
                <div class="song-desc">Struggling to open your heart while lost in the vast past.</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="song-card">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/dreams.jpg" alt="Dreams">
            <div>
                <strong>Dreams — Fleetwood Mac</strong>
                <div class="song-desc">A classic anthem about freedom and the cycles of love.</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="song-card">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/Ironywouldhaveit.jpg" alt="Irony">
            <div>
                <strong>Irony Would Have It — Matt Maltese</strong>
                <div class="song-desc">A beautiful ballad about the unpredictable timing of romance.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</div>

</body>
</html>

